### **In Summary**

> Future web frameworks focus on **speed, modularity, and intelligence.**
> 
> The evolution from simple websites to intelligent, app-like systems has made the web **smarter, faster, and more accessible** than ever.
> 
> Tomorrow’s frameworks will blend **AI, semantic understanding, and cloud scalability** to create a truly intelligent, global web.
